OL,6,FIn a post on social media, Deputy
OL,7,FBurford explains: "After the total
OL,8,Fdestruction of the restaurant last
OL,9,Fyear, various insurance negotiations,
OL,10,Flease limitations and obligations and
OL,11,Fcostings have played a significant
OL,12,Frole in determining a way forward.
OL,14,F"This has ultimately resulted in the
OL,15,Ftransfer of the site to the tenants at
OL,16,Fno cost.
