OL,3,CPolitician sells popular restaurant
OL,4,Csite for #1 after major fire
OL,6,F"While this is not at all the outcome
OL,7,FI would have wanted, it has been a
OL,8,Fcomplex and difficult 18 months and I
OL,9,Fam now free to focus fully on my
OL,10,Fresponsibilities as a people's deputy."
OL,12,FDeputy Burford adds that as President
OL,13,Fof the Planning Authority, she will
OL,14,Frecuse herself from any future
OL,15,Fdiscussions about plans for the site.
OL,17,FThe new owners have another eatery in
OL,18,Ftown and previously outlined their
OL,19,Fintentions to build a new restaurant,
OL,20,Falthough no plans have been submitted
OL,21,Fyet.
